# PROJECT OVERVIEW

The system automatically generates API documentation from GitHub repositories using a locally running LLM (Ollama).

The generated documentation is stored in PostgreSQL along with embeddings.

The system supports Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) by fetching similar documentation before generating new documentation.

The system also includes automatic repository synchronization through scheduled jobs.

